title: Daily Wire Backstage: Ukraine In The Membrane
description:
Can Trump or Biden survive their separate Ukraine scandals? Does Liz Warren's poll surge mean she has more than 1/1024th chance of winning? Has the Left officially driven the next generation insane with climate hysteria? Can entertainment award shows survive woke culture? Is this title's rap reference lost on Shapiro?

Join this roundtable discussion featuring Ben Shapiro, Andrew Klavan, Michael Knowles, Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing as they get to the bottom of these questions and more.
